# Large binary assets — keep on disk, NEVER in the deploy repo (GitHub 2GB
# push-pack limit guard; recurs otherwise). Added 2026-05-30 after a
# `git add .` swept ~2.9GB of TIFF scans, an archive .mov, and 200+ 4K ad
# images into one commit and blocked all pushes. These dir-level excludes
# supersede the older `!nanobanana-output/**/*.jpg` negation above (a file
# under an excluded directory cannot be re-included).
